short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Immerse yourself in the serene atmosphere of a railway station

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The background showcases the warm hues of twilight blending harmoniously with the urban skyline and train tracks, evoking a sense of peace and inspiration. Perfect for those who appreciate the beauty of urban landscapes and the calming allure of nature's golden hour, this extension transforms your browser into a visual masterpiece.

Key features:
- Beautiful background.
- Quick access to frequently visited sites.
- Real-time weather display and clock.
- News
